      <title>无家可归者营地冲突提请美国最高法院审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/homeless-encampment-clash-draws-review-by-us-supreme-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将考虑城市可以在多大程度上阻止无家可归者在公共场所睡觉，并同意听取俄勒冈州一个小镇的上诉，该小镇将使用毯子、枕头或纸板庇护所定为犯罪行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/homeless-encampment-clash-draws-review-by-us-supreme-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:25:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱荷华州党团会议期间最冷的天气威胁着特朗普的领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/coldest-caucuses-ever-threaten-trump-s-lead-as-arctic-blast-hits-iowa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 渴望在周一的爱荷华州共和党党团会议上取得井喷式胜利，而尼基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 和罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 的目标是足够接近领跑者，以延长 2024 年总统竞选的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/coldest-caucuses-ever-threaten-trump-s-lead-as-arctic-blast-hits-iowa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:21:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在最新一轮救济中取消更多学生贷款债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-to-cancel-more-student-loan-debt-in-latest-round-of-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的政府将取消一些借款人的新一批学生贷款债务，这是他在最高法院否决其提供数十亿美元救济的旗舰提案后的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-to-cancel-more-student-loan-debt-in-latest-round-of-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装发射的导弹险些击中俄罗斯石油运输船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/houthis-fire-missile-400-meters-from-russian-oil-carrier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘运输俄罗斯石油的船只险些被也门发射的导弹击中，在对胡塞叛军进行空袭后，船只越来越多地躲避红海。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/houthis-fire-missile-400-meters-from-russian-oil-carrier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得驳回 2018 年视频电话促销诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/trump-wins-dismissal-of-2018-lawsuit-over-video-phone-promotions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着一项审判的结束和下周另一项审判的开始，前总统唐纳德·特朗普在一场低调的诉讼中悄然取得了胜利，这场诉讼已经持续了五年多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/trump-wins-dismissal-of-2018-lawsuit-over-video-phone-promotions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 18:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
